comment: I suspect the reason why Jason Momoa ripped out pages from Amber Heard's books was to prove whether she actually read them or not. The fact that he ripped out pages from several books indicates that she had pretended to finish several of the books, before discovering that pages were missing; it's very likely that he only ripped out pages of books she was actively reading, and stopped as soon as she caught on; anything else would just be vandalism. IOW, Ms. Heard is one of those annoying people who pretend to be great readers, but never actually read. It also means that her mind is so inactive that she can sit for hours, watching and turning pages, without reading them. An active mind would either become so bored as to read the pages, just go do something else, or become so engrossed in deep thought as to forget turning pages and pretending to read. It takes a very special kind of person to remain that passive, and yet sufficiently aware of her surroundings to maintain the pretense. It's almost enough to make me pity her. _Almost._
